quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,79,"Ẹni tó ń fún mi ní jíjẹ, tó ń fún mi ní mímu;"
  26,80,"Àti pé nígbà tí ara mi kò bá yá, Òun l’Ó ń wò mí sàn;"
  26,81,"Ẹni tí Ó máa pa mí, lẹ́yìn náà, Ó máa sọ mí di alààyè;"
  27,52,"Nítorí náà, ìwọ̀nyẹn ni ilé wọn. Ó tí di ilé ahoro nítorí pé wọ́n ṣàbòsí. Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn fún ìjọ tó nímọ̀."
  27,53,"A gba àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo là, tí wọ́n sì ń bẹ̀rù (Allāhu)."
  27,54,"(A tún fi iṣẹ́ ìmísí rán Ànábì) Lūt. (Rántí) nígbà tí ó sọ fún ìjọ rẹ̀ pé: “Ṣé iṣẹ́ aburú ni ẹ óò máa ṣe ni, ẹ sì ríran?"
  28,25,"Ọ̀kan nínú àwọn méjèèjì wá bá a, ó sì ń rìn pẹ̀lú ìtìjú, ó sọ pé: “Dájúdájú bàbá mi ń pè ọ́ nítorí kí ó lè san ọ́ ní ẹ̀san omi tí o fún (àwọn ẹran-ọ̀sìn) wa mu.” Nígbà tí ó dé ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ̀, ó sọ ìtàn (ara rẹ̀) fún un. (Bàbá náà) sọ pé: “Má bẹ̀rù. O ti là lọ́wọ́ ìjọ alábòsí.”"
  28,26,"Ọ̀kan nínú (àwọn ọmọbìnrin) méjèèjì sọ pé: “Bàbá mi o, gbà á síṣẹ́. Dájúdájú ẹni tó dára jùlọ tí o lè gbà síṣẹ́ ni alágbára, olùfọkàntán.”"
  28,27,"Ó sọ pé: “Dájúdájú mo fẹ́ fi ọ̀kan nínú àwọn ọmọbìnrin mi méjèèjì wọ̀nyí fún ọ ní aya lórí (àdéhùn) pé o máa bá mi ṣiṣẹ́ fún ọdún mẹ́jọ. Ṣùgbọ́n tí o bá ṣe é pé ọdún mẹ́wàá, láti ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ nìyẹn. Èmi kò sì fẹ́ kó ìnira bá ọ. Tí Allāhu bá fẹ́, o máa rí mi pé mo wà nínú àwọn ẹni rere.”"